    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2>Refunds & Returns</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>If you are not satisfied with your purchase, please contact us within 7 days of delivery to discuss a return or exchange.</li>
        <li>Refunds or replacements for stock items will be processed once the product is returned in its original condition.</li>
        <li>Custom or personalized items may not be eligible for full refunds unless there is a clear defect or error on our part.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
